            <section id="messaging">
                <div class="section-label">Section 03</div>
                <h2 contenteditable="true">Messaging & Positioning</h2>
                <p class="section-intro" contenteditable="true">Rewritten messaging that shifts from feature-descriptive to outcome-driven, targeting HR decision-makers who buy results, not capabilities.</p>

                <h3>Headline + Subheadline Options</h3>

                <div class="headline-option">
                    <span class="option-tag">Recommended</span>
                    <div class="headline" contenteditable="true">Turn Wellness Programs Into Movements Your Employees Actually Join</div>
                    <div class="subheadline" contenteditable="true">Habit Health's Engagement Engine combines step tracking, team challenges, and smart incentives to drive 3× the participation of traditional wellness programs — without HR doing more work.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="headline-option">
                    <span class="option-tag">Alternative A</span>
                    <div class="headline" contenteditable="true">The Engagement Platform That Makes Health Competitive, Social, and Rewarding</div>
                    <div class="subheadline" contenteditable="true">From daily step streaks to organization-wide leagues, Habit Health turns individual wellness into collective momentum — driving sustained behavior change across your workforce.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="headline-option">
                    <span class="option-tag">Alternative B</span>
                    <div class="headline" contenteditable="true">Your Employees Don't Need Another Wellness App. They Need a Reason to Open It.</div>
                    <div class="subheadline" contenteditable="true">Habit Health's Engagement Engine gives them that reason — with team competitions, peer challenges, live content, and rewards that keep people coming back, not just signing up.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="headline-option">
                    <span class="option-tag">Alternative C — Data-Led</span>
                    <div class="headline" contenteditable="true">From 20% Participation to 70%+ Sustained Engagement</div>
                    <div class="subheadline" contenteditable="true">Most corporate wellness programs see adoption drop by month two. Habit Health's gamified engagement system is built to keep employees active — with challenges, streaks, and rewards that sustain behavior change at scale.</div>
                </div>

                <h3>Feature → Value Rewrites</h3>
                <p contenteditable="true">Every feature on the current site is described in product language. Below is a transformation of each into the language HR buyers respond to.</p>

                <div class="value-transform">
                    <span class="feature-text">Monthly challenges for steps, hydration, posture, and planks</span>
                    <span class="arrow">→</span>
                    <span class="value-text" contenteditable="true">Launch org-wide wellness campaigns in minutes — and watch participation climb week over week</span>
                </div>

                <div class="value-transform">
                    <span class="feature-text">Gamified milestones & digital badges to sustain motivation</span>
                    <span class="arrow">→</span>
                    <span class="value-text" contenteditable="true">Built-in streak mechanics and milestone rewards that turn one-time participants into daily active users</span>
                </div>

                <div class="value-transform">
                    <span class="feature-text">Gamification, nudges, and social features boost participation</span>
                    <span class="arrow">→</span>
                    <span class="value-text" contenteditable="true">A behavioral engagement system — combining team competition, peer accountability, and smart incentives — designed to make healthy habits stick across entire organizations</span>
                </div>

                <div class="value-transform">
                    <span class="feature-text">Habit App integration for live tracking, leaderboards, and rewards</span>
                    <span class="arrow">→</span>
                    <span class="value-text" contenteditable="true">Real-time leaderboards that create organic cross-department competition — with tangible rewards that make winning meaningful</span>
                </div>

                <div class="value-transform">
                    <span class="feature-text">Curated knowledge library</span>
                    <span class="arrow">→</span>
                    <span class="value-text" contenteditable="true">Expert-led webinars, articles, and video content that educate employees while boosting platform engagement</span>
