                <div class="value-transform">
                    <span class="feature-text">Steps Premier League (app screenshot only)</span>
                    <span class="arrow">→</span>
                    <span class="value-text" contenteditable="true">Steps Premier League — an IPL-style corporate step competition where employee teams compete in cricket-themed battles, complete with captains, match days, and live commentary</span>
                </div>

                <div class="callout action">
                    <div class="callout-title">Messaging Principle</div>
                    <p contenteditable="true">Every sentence on the Engagement page should pass the "So What?" test. If an HR leader reads it and thinks "okay, but what does that do for my organization?" — the copy has failed. Tie every feature to participation rates, employee experience, retention, culture, or cost savings.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

