                <div class="callout warning">
                    <div class="callout-title">Competitive Messaging Guidance</div>
                    <p contenteditable="true">Don't name competitors on the website. Instead, use contrast language: "Unlike traditional wellness platforms that offer only admin-led challenges…" or "Most wellness apps stop at tracking. Habit Health starts there." The differentiation should be felt through specificity and naming of unique features (SPL, Peer Challenges) — not through competitor-bashing.</p>
