                        <strong>Add "Engagement" to primary navigation</strong>
                        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:4px 0 0;">Once the /engagement page exists, add it to the nav under "Platform" as the first item. Consider renaming "Wellness Offerings" to "Clinical & Preventive" to reduce confusion.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="tag tag-strategic">Nav Update</span>
                </div>

                <div class="impl-item">
                    <span class="impl-effort medium">Medium</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Source engagement-specific testimonials</strong>
                        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:4px 0 0;">Request 2–3 quotes from HCLT HR contacts specifically about engagement, challenges, or SPL participation. Even informal quotes work if attributed.</p>
